    "date": "2022-01-14T18:03:58Z",
    "text": "Pell Grant Modernization Act \n\nThis bill revises eligibility requirements under the Federal Pell Grant Program.\n\nSpecifically, the bill reduces from 12 to 10 the total number of semesters during which a student may receive a Pell Grant.\n\nIn addition, the bill increases the number of credits that a student must complete each semester in order to be considered a full-time student."
